        <updateDate>2005-04-22T15:00:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p></p> <p>Amends the Controlled Substances Act to provide that any offense of distributing or manufacturing a controlled substance in or near a school, distributing such a substance to a person under age 21, or employing or using a person under age 18 in a drug operation shall constitute a second offense by a person already convicted of any of such offenses.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>A bill to link recidivist penalties for certain drug crimes.</title>
